OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FOvernight, it will remain dry with
OL,8,Ffurther clear spells. A little chilly
OL,9,Fin the countryside but not as cold as
OL,10,Frecent nights. Some misty patches
OL,11,Fpossible in sheltered areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day
OL,14,Fwith possibly some patchy cloud around
OL,15,Fat times. Feeling very warm in the
OL,16,Fsunshine with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
